<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>哨兵 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E5%93%A8%E5%85%B5/</link><description>哨兵 - 标签 - 咔咔不太卡的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://ksmaple.github.io/tags/%E5%93%A8%E5%85%B5/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Redis持久化与高可用</title><link>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/redis%E6%8C%81%E4%B9%85%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%8E%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8/</link><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><author>咔咔</author><guid>https://ksmaple.github.io/posts/%E8%BF%9B%E9%98%B6%E5%B1%82/%E7%BC%93%E5%AD%98%E6%8A%80%E6%9C%AF/redis%E6%8C%81%E4%B9%85%E5%8C%96%E4%B8%8E%E9%AB%98%E5%8F%AF%E7%94%A8/</guid><description><![CDATA[<h1 id="redis持久化与高可用">Redis持久化与高可用</h1>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>核心结论</strong>：Redis通过RDB快照和AOF日志两种持久化方式保障数据安全，RDB适合全量备份和快速恢复，AOF适合实时持久化，生产环境通常同时使用；高可用通过主从复制、哨兵和集群三种架构逐级递进。</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="redis通过rdb快照aof日志实现持久化通过主从复制哨兵集群实现高可用扩展">Redis通过RDB快照+AOF日志实现持久化，通过主从复制+哨兵+集群实现高可用扩展</h2>
<h3 id="持久化rdb与aof的权衡">持久化：RDB与AOF的权衡</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>维度</th>
          <th>RDB</th>
          <th>AOF</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>原理</td>
          <td>定时快照，保存内存数据</td>
          <td>记录每条写命令</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>文件大小</td>
          <td>紧凑（二进制压缩）</td>
          <td>较大（可重写压缩）</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>恢复速度</td>
          <td>快（直接加载内存）</td>
          <td>慢（重放命令）</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>数据安全</td>
          <td>可能丢失最后一次快照</td>
          <td>最多丢失1秒数据（每秒刷盘）</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>性能影响</td>
          <td>快照时fork子进程，短暂阻塞</td>
          <td>持续fsync开销</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>适用场景</td>
          <td>全量备份、灾难恢复</td>
          <td>实时持久化、误操作恢复</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">RDB触发条件（默认）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 900秒内至少1个key变化
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 300秒内至少10个key变化
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 60秒内至少10000个key变化
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">AOF刷盘策略：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- always：每条命令fsync（最安全，最慢）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- everysec：每秒fsync（默认，平衡）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- no：由OS决定（最快，最不安全）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">混合持久化（Redis 4.0+）：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- AOF文件包含RDB前缀 + 增量AOF命令
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 重写时先生成RDB，再追加后续命令
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 兼顾恢复速度和数据安全</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="主从复制读写分离的基础">主从复制：读写分离的基础</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">主从复制流程：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. 从节点发送 SYNC 命令
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 主节点执行 BGSAVE，生成RDB文件
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. 主节点发送RDB文件给从节点
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">4. 从节点加载RDB，清空旧数据
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">5. 主节点将复制期间的写命令缓存到replication buffer
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">6. 发送buffer中的命令给从节点
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">7. 后续持续同步：主节点写命令异步发送给从节点
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">复制方式：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 全量复制：初次同步或主从断开过久
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">- 部分复制（PSYNC 2.0+）：基于复制偏移量，只同步差异</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="哨兵sentinel自动故障转移">哨兵（Sentinel）：自动故障转移</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">Sentinel架构：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       ┌─────────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       │ Client  │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">       └────┬────┘
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">            │ 连接Sentinel获取主节点地址
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">            ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ┌───────┴───────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │  Sentinel-1   │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │  Sentinel-2   │  （至少3个，奇数个）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │  Sentinel-3   │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    └───────┬───────┘
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">            │ 监控 + 自动故障转移
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">            ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ┌───────┴───────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │    Master     │  ← 主节点（写）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    └───────┬───────┘
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">            │ 复制
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ┌───────┴───────┐
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │   Slave-1     │  ← 从节点（读）
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    │   Slave-2     │
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    └───────────────┘
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Sentinel职责：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">1. 监控：周期性检查主从节点健康
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">2. 通知：故障时通知管理员或其他应用
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">3. 自动故障转移：主节点宕机，选举从节点为新主
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">4. 配置提供者：客户端向Sentinel查询当前主节点地址</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<h3 id="集群cluster水平扩展">集群（Cluster）：水平扩展</h3>
<div class="code-block code-line-numbers open" style="counter-reset: code-block 0">
    <div class="code-header language-">
        <span class="code-title"><i class="arrow fas fa-angle-right" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="ellipses"><i class="fas fa-ellipsis-h" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
        <span class="copy" title="复制到剪贴板"><i class="far fa-copy" aria-hidden="true"></i></span>
    </div><div class="highlight"><pre tabindex="0" class="chroma"><code class="language-fallback" data-lang="fallback"><span class="line"><span class="cl">Redis Cluster架构：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">采用哈希槽（Hash Slot）分片，共16384个槽
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Master-A (0-5460)    Master-B (5461-10922)    Master-C (10923-16383)
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">    ↓                        ↓                         ↓
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"> Slave-A1                 Slave-B1                  Slave-C1
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"> Slave-A2                 Slave-B2                  Slave-C2
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Key路由：CRC16(key) % 16384 → 确定槽 → 确定节点
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">Moved重定向：
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  客户端请求Key到错误节点 → 返回MOVED slot ip:port
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">  客户端更新槽映射，重新请求</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<hr>
<h2 id="实际应用中的决策与权衡">实际应用中的决策与权衡</h2>
<table>
  <thead>
      <tr>
          <th>场景</th>
          <th>架构</th>
          <th>容量</th>
          <th>可用性</th>
      </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
      <tr>
          <td>缓存、可重建</td>
          <td>单实例 + RDB</td>
          <td>内存限制</td>
          <td>低</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>读多写少</td>
          <td>主从 + 哨兵</td>
          <td>内存限制</td>
          <td>高</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>大数据量</td>
          <td>集群</td>
          <td>线性扩展</td>
          <td>高</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
          <td>跨机房</td>
          <td>主从跨机房</td>
          <td>内存限制</td>
          <td>异地灾备</td>
      </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>
<hr>
<h2 id="常见问题与误区">常见问题与误区</h2>
<h3 id="问题1主从复制延迟导致数据不一致">问题1：主从复制延迟导致数据不一致</h3>
<p><strong>根因</strong>：网络延迟、从节点处理慢
<strong>解决</strong>：监控复制偏移量、强制读主库（关键读）、延迟阈值告警</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>